An action function this refers to the current pipe scope this, in fact it is the same as a native JavaScript. It should be noted that At the same time a single action can have more than one state of synchronization changes, and each change will be a view of the status update, if you need an action to update only a number of synchronized changes, you can use batch API so that it performs an update.
And then we've got the next few action.
